ATBU Graduates 8,495, 118 Students Emerge With First Class. The Abubakar Tafawa Balewa University (ATBU), Bauchi, will at its 23rd to 25th convocation ceremony scheduled for May 12th, 2018 graduate a total of 8,495 students. This was disclosed by the Vice Chancellor of the University, Prof. Saminu Abdurahman Ibrahim, during a press briefing at the Gubi … The post ATBU Graduates 8,495, 118 Students Emerge With First Class appeared first on Students Nigeria.   Follow us on twitter @NigeriaTodayNG Also, Like us on facebook This post was syndicated from Students Nigeria. Click here to read the full text on the original website.